  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anime Play Life: Unlimited</strong> is a cozy anime-style life simulation about leaving the busy city behind and starting a new chapter in the idyllic village of Yakuta.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle into a calm environment, find a part-time job at a local restaurant, spend your free time on relaxing activities like fishing, and explore nearby locations. Visit surrounding towns and special places, including your grandparents’ estate, set in a peaceful winter landscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on relaxing gameplay, exploration, and the freedom to enjoy a calm, peaceful experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seasonal Interactions</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience small seasonal moments, like writing a letter to Santa during winter.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.poster.avif?t=1768392640\" width=1000 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.webm?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.mp4?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>A Cozy Part-Time Job</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From placing toppings to finishing the order — enjoy a calm and satisfying pizza-making experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/7190c74e5a64d3ab3098b3adfce5fbfc.poster.avif?t=1768392640\" width=1000 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/7190c74e5a64d3ab3098b3adfce5fbfc.webm?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/7190c74e5a64d3ab3098b3adfce5fbfc.mp4?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create Your Own Space</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and customize your surroundings freely and creatively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/86503f5e4654688889e12da8a3c7d69d.poster.avif?t=1768392640\" width=1000 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/86503f5e4654688889e12da8a3c7d69d.webm?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/86503f5e4654688889e12da8a3c7d69d.mp4?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anime Play Life: Unlimited</strong> is a cozy anime-style life simulation about leaving the busy city behind and starting a new chapter in the idyllic village of Yakuta.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle into a calm environment, find a part-time job at a local restaurant, spend your free time on relaxing activities like fishing, and explore nearby locations. Visit surrounding towns and special places, including your grandparents’ estate, set in a peaceful winter landscape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on relaxing gameplay, exploration, and the freedom to enjoy a calm, peaceful experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seasonal Interactions</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience small seasonal moments, like writing a letter to Santa during winter.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.poster.avif?t=1768392640\" width=1000 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.webm?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/4ac00b48cd7e7b43ee4e865c99fa384c.mp4?t=1768392640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>A Cozy Part-Time Job</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From placing toppings to finishing the order — enjoy a calm and satisfying pizza-making experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379320/extras/7190c74e5a64d3ab3098b3adfce5fbfc.poster.avif?t=1768392640\" width=1000 height=460 ><source src=\"https://